The paper focuses on document image analysis using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the challenges of reproducibility in machine learning, which suggests that it could also belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. Additionally, the paper mentions natural language processing (cs.CL) and information retrieval (cs.IR) as potential areas of application for the framework. Finally, since the framework is implemented using the PyTorch deep learning library, it could also belong to the deep learning (cs.DL) sub-category.
